---
title: Easy Creamy Bacon & Garlic Farfalle with Mixed Salad & Parmesan Cheese
description: Farfalle – there are so many delights in cooking with this fun bow-tie pasta. And the most delightful part about tonight's dish,
you ask? The fact that this mouth-watering and creamy sensation is ready in 15 minutes! It can't get any better than this.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/nz-easy-creamy-bacon-garlic-farfalle-c9a5e8e2.jpg
